title: Fantasy Forest
description: Step into a magical world with this incredible Fantasy Forest Environment!
longDescription:
VIDEO TRAILER | DEMO | PHYSICS WORLD DEMO | DOCUMENTATION


Step into our Dark Fantasy Forest Environment with two captivating levels: a serene, lush Peaceful Forest, and an eerie, fog-filled Scary Swamp.

Both levels are game-ready with interactive foliage and dynamic effects to enhance your adventure!


This comprehensive package includes:

  • An impressive collection of 99 static meshes, each with a secondary moss material!
  • A Foliage Physics System paired with a dynamic wind system, bringing your plants to life!
  • Dynamic grass and mud that leave trails behind your characters!



BONUS - Pro Alien Physics World

This asset includes the Pro version of our Physics System and the two additional Environments that come with it.

You'll gain a wealth of added content, such as planet shaders, glowing grass systems, footsteps, lightning and rain effects, and much more!



Foliage Physics

Our advanced foliage physics system intelligently detects nearby plants and seamlessly converts them into interactive blueprints.

It's highly efficient, enriching your world with dynamic and engaging vegetation.



Moss & Rock Variations

All Trees, logs, stumps, rocks, ruins, and mushrooms have 2 material types - Mossy and Bare.

This moss material is procedurally generated using ambient occlusion and normal maps, ensuring that the moss is always on the top of the mesh regardless of rotation.



Animated Fairies

Bring life you your forest with our spline animated fairy blueprint.

Simply drag your spline path around your level, set your speed variables and fairy color, and away your fairy will fly!



Footstep Sounds

Automatically detect the surface beneath your player and play the right footstep sound.

There are 29 ground sounds like dirt, grass, mud, and sand, plus 16 water footstep sounds.



Music

As a bonus, this package includes three cinematic musical tracks, totaling 15 minutes of playtime.

Download the demo and listen to them with our in-built music player!



Texture Resolution & Performance

All textures are provided at a minimum resolution of 4096x4096, suitable for film-quality environments.

However, they are pre-configured to the lowest reasonable settings, typically 2048 or lower, to ensure high detail without sacrificing performance.

IMPORTANT NOTE:

This product will not work unless you first move the "FoliagePhysics" folder into your contents folder.

Simply close your unreal project, cut the "FoliagePhysics" folder from inside the "AlienJunglePlants" folder, and paste into your "Contents" folder. Then open your project again and everything will work correctly!
